     H            Y.
     H** UTLR65 ***********************************************************
     H*  ADJUST BLANK (*BCAT)
     H*----------------------------------------------------*
     H*  CALLING SEQ.
     H*                    CALL 'UTLR65'
     H*                    PARM           $IN   100
     H*                    PARM           $OUT  100
     H*                    PARM           $RTN    1
     H*   IN  $IN    100A  SOURCE
     H*   OUT $OUT   100A  RESULT
     H*       $RTN     1A  RETURN (BLANK: OK, *: ERROR)
     H*
     H*   EX.
     H*   $IN = '    ABC  D  EFG    '
     H*   $OUT= 'ABC D EFG          '
      *********************************************************************
     E                    IN        100  1
     E                    OT        100  1
      ******************************************************************
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           $IN   100
     C                     PARM           $OUT  100
     C                     PARM           $RTN    1
      *
     C                     MOVEA$IN       IN
     C                     MOVEA*BLANK    OT
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    $OUT
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    $RTN
     C                     Z-ADD0         IX      30
     C                     Z-ADD0         IY      30
     C                     MOVE 'Y'       IGFLG   1
      *
     C           1         DO   100       IX
      * IGNORE
     C           IX        IFGT 100
     C                     ITER
     C                     ENDIF
      * IGNORE
     C           IGFLG     IFEQ 'Y'
     C           IN,IX     ANDEQ*BLANK
     C                     ITER
     C                     ENDIF
      * MOVE
     C                     MOVE 'N'       IGFLG
     C                     ADD  1         IY
     C                     MOVELIN,IX     OT,IY
      * SET IGNORE FLAG
     C           IGFLG     IFEQ 'N'
     C           IN,IX     ANDEQ*BLANK
     C                     MOVE 'Y'       IGFLG
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     C                     MOVEAOT        $OUT
      *
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
